show.description: ISO ki scientist Anjali Kaal Asur ki puja karti hai aur bacchon ki bali chadati hai par Mars mission par apne “soul-mate” Vikram Sharma ko haasil karne ke liye khoon, blame aur kala jadoo tak karti hai. Kya hoga jab dusri scientist Priya aayegi Anjali aur Vikram ke raaste?
